flowchart LR
    A[Developer Push or PR] --> B[GitHub Actions: CI Workflow]
    B --> C[dart format --set-exit-if-changed .]
    C --> D{Formatting clean?}
    D -->|No| E[Fail CI\nRequest formatting fixes]
    D -->|Yes| F[flutter analyze]
    F --> G{Analyzer clean?}
    G -->|No| H[Fail CI\nFix code issues]
    G -->|Yes| I[flutter test]
    I --> J{All tests pass?}
    J -->|No| K[Fail CI\nDebug regressions]
    J -->|Yes| L[CI Success\nReady for release flow]
